  "texts": [
    "The F-One Chatbot, developed in this project, can be considered to belong to both categories.",
    "This is made possible by combining the features of Text-Generation models and Information-Retrieval models.",
    "This combination allows for overcoming the main limitations of both models while leveraging their capabilities.Retrieval-based models rely on predefined responses, chosen from a set of options.",
    "They ensure meaningful content, but they require manual input or selection of responses, which can be time-consuming.",
    "Such Chatbots excel in answering specific topics, making them valuable for tailored business Chatbots."
